title: SnippetsLab 1.4.1 [MAC OS X]
description:
MADE IN UKRAINE

SnippetsLab 1.4.1 - Easy-to-use code snippets manager. It helps you to collect and organize valuable code snippets, and makes sure that you have easy access to them whenever you want.

SnippetsLab makes it simple to manage all of your valuable code snippets in one place with nested folders, tags and Smart Groups support. And you can sort your snippets by date, title, and more.
SnippetsLab features syntax highlighting with a wide range of supported languages. Choose your favorite ones out of more than 250 available languages.

What's new in version 1.4.1:
- Added support for OS X services.
- Added keyboard shortcuts for copying the snippet and switching between folders / tags.
- Added the ability to define your own keyboard shortcuts for syntax coloring modes.
- Several minor bug fixes and enhancements.

MADE IN UKRAINE
